OL,3,CInvestigations after fatal-crash near
OL,4,CNewton Stewart
OL,6,FA woman has died in a crash on the
OL,7,FA714 between Newton Stewart and
OL,8,FWigtown.
OL,10,FPolice Scotland say it happened at
OL,11,Faround 9:35am on Wednesday 3 June. The
OL,12,F65-year-old was pronounced dead at the
OL,13,Fscene.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/4
