PN,35402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1780758677
OL,3,CInvestigations after fatal-crash near
OL,4,CNewton Stewart
OL,6,FThe collision involved a Suzuki S-
OL,7,FCross and a Volkswagen Golf. The woman
OL,8,Fwho died was a passenger in the
OL,9,FSuzuki. A 72-year-old man driving the
OL,10,Fvehicle was airlifted to hospital in
OL,11,FGlasgow and a 34-year-old woman
OL,12,Fdriving the Volkswagen was taken to
OL,13,FDumfries and Galloway Royal infirmary.
OL,15,FThe section of the A714 has now
OL,16,Freopened following crash
OL,17,Finvestigations.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/4
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
