FL,355,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1780758677
OL,3,CInvestigations after fatal-crash near
OL,4,CNewton Stewart
OL,6,FSergeant Lindsey Tait said: "Our
OL,7,Fthoughts are with the family of the
OL,8,Fwoman who has died at what is a very
OL,9,Fdifficult time.
OL,11,F"Our enquiries are ongoing to
OL,12,Festablish the full circumstances, and
OL,13,Fwe are asking anyone who saw what
OL,14,Fhappened to get in touch.
OL,16,F"If you were driving in the area at
OL,17,Fthe time please check any dash-cam
OL,18,Ffootage you have as any images
OL,19,Fcaptured could assist with our
OL,20,Finvestigation."
